            <p class="text-body-lg" style="color:var(--color-muted-foreground);max-width:65ch;margin-top:16px;">Every field trip produces a comprehensive safety binder. This is what your school board will see when they ask about trip safety documentation.</p>

            <!-- Checklist -->
